  <h1 class="page-title fade-in">Dallas <em>allergy</em> season,<br>explained.</h1>
  <p class="page-subtitle fade-in">Cedar, ragweed, and oak affect millions across Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite, and Irving every year. Here's what triggers what — and the treatments that actually provide lasting relief in North Texas.</p>
</section>
